# Per-miner overlay for ./run_miner.sh -P miner-12
# PureMakerV4Agent: all-book maker (at-touch + cushioned reprice + never-cut), activity floor REVERTED
# (flat books idle at kappa=None / free-dropped, like V1/V2/AR — V3's force-seed was a net-loss regression).
